This package contains an init-script for booting into ARP2-UAE
directly from GRUB.

A sample GRUB configuration entry:

title ARP2-UAE
        root (hd0,6)
        kernel /boot/vmlinuz-2.6.13-1.1526_FC4 ro root=LABEL=/1 rhgb quiet plip=0 init=/opt/arp2/sbin/init
        initrd /boot/initrd-2.6.13-1.1526_FC4.img
